{
  "stem": "166.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 221.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We worked in this camp a year, and later on when, when we worked at the camp we marched with the, with guards out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the, in the, factory, inside, we were free, because they couldn't-- they didn't have so many guards to guard each electrician.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If they would work with a shovel in the hard work, they had a guard with them there all the time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But with electricians, we, we had to come to the gate of the factory at the end of the day and wait for the whole colony, for the whole group, and then we marched into the camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I worked there with other-- two more guys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was especially in the IG Farben-- in the [NON-ENGLISH] controller-- I worked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] controller-- they kind of were in charge for the thermal couples and to see that the gas has the right temperature on the, on the towers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And over there-- when we come home from work in the camp, they grabbed a few guys here and a few guys there to go unload trains with gravel after work or on a Saturday, to do this all day long.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then I spoke to my boss.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Maybe you make me work-- I like to work Saturdays here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't want to go into the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He asked me why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I tell him, because I-- it's no good in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We don't have any food there, and it's, it's hard work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the boss over there made me come in with the two other guys what they worked in the IG Farben industry, especially Saturday, to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole camp was-- did not work, and we three of us came in, and we worked Saturday.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
